content: Head back up the main path through more Frozen Corpses, taking them on one at a time so you don't get overwhelmed. Once you reach the top of this area you'll find a large snowy field where the monkey is waiting for you.

The content is as follows:
Head back up the main path through more Frozen Corpses, taking them on one at a time so you don't get overwhelmed. Once you reach the top of this area you'll find a large snowy field where the monkey is waiting for you.
